我只能捡她不要而剩下的破烂

1087
01:19:08,556 --> 01:19:12,268
I've come to terms with that, Daffs,
why can't you?
我都可以接受了,大卫,为何你不行?

1088
01:19:12,309 --> 01:19:15,688
Lizzie, I want you to know
that my feelings for you...
小丽,我要你明白我对你的感情...

1089
01:19:15,729 --> 01:19:19,900
David! There are slightly more
pressing matters at hand here.
大卫! 现在有更加危急的事

1090
01:19:19,984 --> 01:19:24,113
- Like "Daffs" pointing a gun at my mum.
- I'm not being unreasonable, "Pickle".
-对,就像“懦夫”拿枪指着我妈
-失去理性的可不是我,“泡菜”

1091
01:19:24,196 --> 01:19:27,241
- Christ, she's not dead!
- She's finished.
-老天,她还没死!
-她完了

1092
01:19:27,324 --> 01:19:29,410
For a hero, you're quite a hypocrite.
要当英雄,你真够虚伪了

1093
01:19:29,451 --> 01:19:32,204
You've gone from
a chartered accountant to Charlton Heston.
你被却尔登希斯顿开除了
特约会计师一职

1094
01:19:32,246 --> 01:19:34,081
I'm not a chartered accountant.
我不是特约会计师

1095
01:19:34,123 --> 01:19:36,333
- Well, you look like one.
- Yeah.
-你看起来就像
-没错

1096
01:19:36,417 --> 01:19:39,420
- I'm a lecturer.
- You're a twat.
-我是个讲师
-你是个不折不扣的白痴

1097
01:19:39,503 --> 01:19:43,174
She's not your mum.
In a minute she'll be just another zombie.
她不再是你妈了
她马上就会变成另一具僵尸

1098
01:19:43,257 --> 01:19:46,427
- Don't say that.
- We're not using the Z word.
