-我们不用“僵”开头那个字

1099
01:19:46,510 --> 01:19:50,431
Please can we just calm the fuck down!
拜他妈的冷静下来!

1100
01:19:52,016 --> 01:19:55,644
Now, I can see what David is trying to say...
我明白大卫想说什么...

1101
01:19:55,686 --> 01:19:57,980
- Thank you.
- Even if he is being a twat.
-谢谢
-就算他是个白痴

1102
01:19:58,063 --> 01:19:59,857
Yep.
对

1103
01:19:59,940 --> 01:20:02,818
And, Shaun... Shaun, look at me.
肖恩... 肖恩,看着我

1104
01:20:05,613 --> 01:20:09,200
I can't begin to imagine
how hard this must be for you
我无法想像这对你有多难受

1105
01:20:09,283 --> 01:20:11,702
but we can't afford to fall apart.
但我们不能再分化下去

1106
01:20:12,870 --> 01:20:15,706
Shaun, babe...
肖恩,宝贝...

1107
01:20:15,789 --> 01:20:18,792
I know you don't wanna hear this...
我知道你不想听这种话...

1108
01:20:37,186 --> 01:20:39,230
You do it.
你来

1109
01:20:49,198 --> 01:20:51,283
I'm sorry, Mum.
抱歉了,妈

1110
01:20:52,660 --> 01:20:55,037
Do it!
开枪!

1111
01:21:10,052 --> 01:21:14,557
Well...I think we're all agreed,
you did the right thing there.
我想我们一致同意你做了正确的事

1112
01:21:20,271 --> 01:21:22,606
David, no!
大卫,不!

1113
01:21:23,524 --> 01:21:24,817
David!
大卫!

1114
01:21:24,942 --> 01:21:27,528
- Right, I'm leaving.
- What?
-好,我要走了
-什么?

1115
01:21:27,528 --> 01:21:30,114
- I'm not staying here.
- David, it's suicide.
-我不要待在这里
-大卫,你这是去自杀

1116
01:21:31,907 --> 01:21:35,327
- I think you should go.
