-我觉得你该走
-我们会的,我们懂得自我防御

1117
01:21:35,369 --> 01:21:37,830
- What do you mean "we"?
- What do you mean?
-你是指"我们"吗?
-什么意思?

1118
01:21:37,872 --> 01:21:41,750
Opening that door now
would be a very silly thing to do.
现在打开那扇门会是非常愚蠢的行为

1119
01:21:41,834 --> 01:21:44,211
- You gonna stay here with him?
- Look...
-你想留下来陪他吗?
-听着...

1120
01:21:44,295 --> 01:21:46,547
- After where he led us?
- Let me finish!
-在他带我们来这儿后还想吗?
-让我把话说完!

1121
01:21:46,589 --> 01:21:50,718
Shaun didn't ask you to come here.
You came for the same reason I did.
肖恩并没要求你来
你来的理由跟我是一样的

1122
01:21:50,759 --> 01:21:53,554
- Get away from that door this instant!
- But...
-马上离那扇门远一点!
-可是...

1123
01:21:53,637 --> 01:21:55,473
David!
大卫!

1124
01:22:02,980 --> 01:22:05,107
I'm so sorry, Dianne.
我很抱歉,黛安

1125
01:22:05,149 --> 01:22:09,236
Maybe I'm not the one
you should be apologising to.
也许你该道歉的人不是我

1126
01:22:11,739 --> 01:22:13,699
Shaun...
肖恩...

1127
01:22:18,871 --> 01:22:20,789
David! No!
大卫! 不!

1128
01:22:20,831 --> 01:22:23,167
No! No! No!
不! 不! 不!

1129
01:22:25,002 --> 01:22:26,921
David!
大卫!

1130
01:22:27,505 --> 01:22:29,673
- No! No!
- David!
-不! 不!
-大卫!

1131
01:22:50,611 --> 01:22:52,738
David!
大卫!

1132
01:22:53,447 --> 01:22:55,115
Dianne, no!
黛安,不!

1133
01:22:55,199 --> 01:22:56,784
I'm coming, David!
我来了,大卫!

1134
01:23:00,079 --> 01:23:02,540
David!
大卫!

1135
01:23:02,623 --> 01:23:04,458
Oh dear.
老天

1136
01:23:04,542 --> 01:23:06,710
- Cocktails?
- Do it.
-鸡尾酒?
-动手吧

1137
01:23:17,638 --> 01:23:19,390
Stay back!
退后!

1138
01:23:24,562 --> 01:23:26,397
Shaun, hold them!
肖恩,挡住他们!

1139
01:23:29,567 --> 01:23:31,402
Heads!
前面!

1140
01:23:35,322 --> 01:23:37,199
- Ed!
- Hurry up!
-艾德!
-快!

1141
01:23:38,993 --> 01:23:41,412
Shauny, look who it is.
肖恩,你看谁来了

1142
01:23:41,495 --> 01:23:44,039
Fuck-a-doodle-doo!
操他奶奶的!

1143
01:23:45,583 --> 01:23:47,251
Ed!
艾德!

1144
01:23:47,334 --> 01:23:49,253
- Shaun!
- Ed!
-肖恩!
-艾德!

1145
01:23:49,336 --> 01:23:51,297
Don't groan at me, you thick fuck!
少朝我低吼,你这超级混蛋!

1146
01:23:51,338 --> 01:23:53,174
I can't hold them!
我挡不住了!

1147
01:23:56,844 --> 01:23:58,220
No!
不!

1148
01:24:02,349 --> 01:24:04,101
- Shaun!
- Pete!
-肖恩!
-彼得!

1149
01:24:06,270 --> 01:24:08,189
I said leave him alone!
我说放过他!

1150
01:24:11,358 --> 01:24:14,320
Ed. Ed!
艾德,艾德!

1151
01:24:14,361 --> 01:24:17,448
Shaun, bar!
肖恩,进吧!

1152
01:24:28,542 --> 01:24:30,419
Ed!
艾德!

1153
01:24:31,295 --> 01:24:33,172
Ed!
艾德!

1154
01:24:33,839 --> 01:24:36,509
Ed!
艾德!

1155
01:24:36,509 --> 01:24:38,427
What?
什么事?

1156
01:24:38,469 --> 01:24:40,721
Chuck us a cloth, will you?
给我一块布,好吗?

1157
01:24:53,901 --> 01:24:56,403
- Where are the shells?
- They're on the bar.
-弹药呢?
-在吧上

1158
01:24:56,487 --> 01:24:58,989
Oh, fuck.
哦,干

1159
01:25:01,325 --> 01:25:02,952
Fuck it!
干!

1160
01:25:03,035 --> 01:25:05,913
What are we gonna do?
Where are we gonna go?
我们怎么办? 要去哪呀?

1161
01:25:05,996 --> 01:25:08,457
- The cellar.
- Maybe we can get out!
-地下室
-也许我们能逃出去!

1162
01:25:08,499 --> 01:25:13,462
- There's a hatch out on to the street.
- You mean go back outside?
-有升降装置通到外面街道
-你是说回外面去?

1163
01:25:13,504 --> 01:25:16,340
Oh, give us a fucking break!
哦,他妈的饶了我们吧!

1164
01:25:22,346 --> 01:25:24,557
Go!
走!

1165
01:25:34,108 --> 01:25:36,318
I can see the street.
我可以看到街道

1166
01:25:37,444 --> 01:25:38,779
Come on.
快点

1167
01:25:40,197 --> 01:25:42,283
Come on!
快点!

1168
01:25:43,200 --> 01:25:45,828
Why won't it open?
怎么打不开呀?

1169
01:25:55,796 --> 01:26:00,050
That's it then, we're trapped.
"Hey, let's go to the Winchester!"
就这样了,我们被困住了
“嘿,我们去温彻斯特吧!”

1170
01:26:00,134 --> 01:26:02,011
Whose fucking idea was that?
那是谁该死的主意啊?

1171
01:26:02,052 --> 01:26:04,889
Man, I've really ballsed this up.
我真的搞砸了

1172
01:26:08,392 --> 01:26:12,021
- No, you haven't.
- I have, Liz. I couldn't save us.
-不,你没有
-我有,丽兹,我救不了我们

1173
01:26:12,062 --> 01:26:16,859
I couldn't save Di or David.
I couldn't even save Mum. I'm useless.
我救不了小黛或大卫
甚至救不了我妈,我真没用

1174
01:26:16,901 --> 01:26:22,573
You shouldn't feel so responsible, you tried.
You did something, that's what counts.
你不该这么自责,你试过了
你尽了力,那点才重要

1175
01:26:24,575 --> 01:26:26,660
Yeah, I suppose.
大概吧

1176
01:26:29,163 --> 01:26:31,916
Do you think they'll get through?
你想他们会进来吗?

1177
01:26:31,999 --> 01:26:33,834
Yeah.
是的

1178
01:26:35,252 --> 01:26:37,505
How many shells have we got left?
还剩多少弹药?

1179
01:26:37,588 --> 01:26:40,716
Erm...two.
嗯...两发

1180
01:26:40,758 --> 01:26:45,888
I suppose we could take a few of them out
if they stand in a line.
我想如果他们排成一排的话
可以解决掉好几个

1181
01:26:45,930 --> 01:26:48,140
I wasn't thinking about them.
我不是在想他们

1182
01:26:48,182 --> 01:26:49,934
I know.
我知道

1183
01:26:54,939 --> 01:26:59,568
- What about Ed? There's only two shells.
- I don't mind being eaten.
-艾德怎么办? 只剩两发弹药
-我不介意被吃掉

1184
01:27:03,447 --> 01:27:05,866
How are we gonna do this?
我们要怎样做?

1185
01:27:05,950 --> 01:27:08,619
I don't know. Erm...
不清楚...

1186
01:27:08,702 --> 01:27:10,746
One of us has to go first.
我们其中一人必须先死

1187
01:27:10,830 --> 01:27:13,999
One should do the other
and then do themselves.
一个人射另一个人,然后再对付他们

1188
01:27:14,041 --> 01:27:17,086
You should do me.
I'll muck it up if I have to do myself.
该由你来射我
要我自己来的话我会失败的

1189
01:27:26,220 --> 01:27:29,557
I don't think I've got it in me
to shoot my flatmate,
我不想在同一个晚上...

1190
01:27:29,598 --> 01:27:33,018
my mum and my girlfriend
all in the same evening.
射杀我的室友、我妈和我女朋友

1191
01:27:34,395 --> 01:27:36,605
What makes you think I've taken you back?
你怎会认为我又接纳你了?

1192
01:27:36,647 --> 01:27:38,524
Well...
嗯...

1193
01:27:39,650 --> 01:27:41,986
you don't want to die single, do you?
你不想死了还是单身吧?

1194
01:27:42,069 --> 01:27:45,823
Actually...I would like to be shot.
事实上...我愿意被开枪打死

1195
01:27:46,907 --> 01:27:51,287
Besides, I've changed. I haven't had a fag
since yesterday, I promise.
此外,我变了,我从昨天起
就没抽过一根菸,我保证

1196
01:27:51,328 --> 01:27:53,455
He hasn't.
他没抽

1197
01:27:55,166 --> 01:27:57,501
Maybe we should have one now.
也许我们现在该抽一根

1198
01:28:00,838 --> 01:28:03,841
- You left them in my flat.
- Yeah, in the bin.
-你留在我公寓的
-对,我丢掉的

1199
01:28:03,924 --> 01:28:06,927
- I was desperate.
- Sneaky monkey.
-我当时心情很差
-死猴子

1200
01:28:07,011 --> 01:28:10,222
- Sorry.
- I won't say anything.
-抱歉
-没关系

1201
01:28:22,610 --> 01:28:24,987
Come on, we're getting out of here.
快点,我们要离开了

1202
01:28:26,030 --> 01:28:28,991
- I might just stay here.
- But we can get out.
-我只想待在这里
-但我们出的去了

1203
01:28:29,033 --> 01:28:32,578
- You two should make a go of it.
- What are you talking about?
-你们俩应该离开
-你在说什么呀?

1204
01:28:32,661 --> 01:28:35,998
- I only hold you back.
- Yeah, but...
-我只会拖累你
-对,不过...

1205
01:28:41,879 --> 01:28:43,881
Maybe you should have this.
也许枪该留给你

1206
01:28:45,216 --> 01:28:46,967
- Don't you want it?
- No.
-你不要吗?
-不要

1207
01:28:47,051 --> 01:28:49,970
I can't hit anything with it anyway,
I'm rubbish.
反正我也打不中,我枪法太烂了

1208
01:28:53,390 --> 01:28:56,894
- Ed, I'm sorry.
- What for?
-艾德,对不起
-为什么?

1209
01:28:56,977 --> 01:29:01,774
- Cos I was shouting at you earlier on.
- It's all right.
-因为我稍早前对你大吼大叫
-没关系

1210
01:29:01,857 --> 01:29:04,151
I'm sorry too.
我也很对不起

1211
01:29:04,235 --> 01:29:06,278
It's OK.
不要紧了

1212
01:29:06,320 --> 01:29:08,072
No...
不...

1213
01:29:08,113 --> 01:29:10,199
I'm sorry, Shaun.
对不起,肖恩

1214
01:29:13,077 --> 01:29:16,288
Oh, God! That's not funny.
老天! 不好玩

1215
01:29:16,330 --> 01:29:21,252
- I'll stop doing 'em when you stop laughing.
- I'm not laughing.
-你不笑我就不会这样做了
-我没在笑

1216
01:29:33,848 --> 01:29:35,641
You'd better be off.
你们最好快走

1217
01:29:45,442 --> 01:29:47,736
Bye, Ed. Love you.
拜,艾德,爱你

1218
01:29:48,612 --> 01:29:50,197
Cheers.
加油

1219
01:29:51,198 --> 01:29:53,284
I love you too, man.
我也爱你,老弟

1220
01:29:56,453 --> 01:29:58,539
Gay.
玻璃

1221
01:30:19,477 --> 01:30:21,854
- Ready?
